  <VFEE_ArtExhibit.questContentRules.rulesStrings.25>raidArrivedLetterLabel-&gt;Deserter assasination attempt</VFEE_ArtExhibit.questContentRules.rulesStrings.25>
  <VFEE_ArtExhibit.questContentRules.rulesStrings.26>raidArrivedLetterText-&gt;A group of deserters have arrived to attempt to disrupt the art exhibit and assasinate the royals\n\n[asker_nameFull] does not care for the threat and demands the exhibit continues!  [asker_possessive] wants you too keep them safe and deal with the &quot;peasants&quot;.</VFEE_ArtExhibit.questContentRules.rulesStrings.26>
  <VFEE_ArtExhibit.questContentRules.rulesStrings.27>ArtExhibitSuccessLetterLabel-&gt;Exhibit Success</VFEE_ArtExhibit.questContentRules.rulesStrings.27>
  <VFEE_ArtExhibit.questContentRules.rulesStrings.28>ArtExhibitSuccessLetterText-&gt;The shuttle has departed with [asker_nameFull] and [asker_possessive] guests. Overall the event was a success and everyone made it back safe.</VFEE_ArtExhibit.questContentRules.rulesStrings.28>
  <VFEE_ArtExhibit.questContentRules.rulesStrings.3>CeremonyFailedLetterLabel-&gt;Art Exhibit failed</VFEE_ArtExhibit.questContentRules.rulesStrings.3>
  <VFEE_ArtExhibit.questContentRules.rulesStrings.4>CeremonyFailedLetterText-&gt;[asker_nameFull] is disappointed by your failure to make for an enjoyable exhibit. [asker_pronoun] is leaving with [asker_possessive] guests</VFEE_ArtExhibit.questContentRules.rulesStrings.4>
  <VFEE_ArtExhibit.questContentRules.rulesStrings.5>CeremonyTimeoutLetterLabel-&gt;Art Exhibit failed</VFEE_ArtExhibit.questContentRules.rulesStrings.5>
  <VFEE_ArtExhibit.questContentRules.rulesStrings.6>CeremonyTimeoutLetterText-&gt;[asker_nameFull] has grown tired of waiting for you to start the exhibit. [asker_pronoun] is leaving with [asker_possessive] guests.</VFEE_ArtExhibit.questContentRules.rulesStrings.6>
